);\n            }\n            group.shutdownGracefully(0L, 5L, TimeUnit.SECONDS).sync();\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 942, "output": 843, "cacheRead": 18944, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 20729, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777390868754, "responseId": "resp_000681f8252d408a0169f0d51537c0819ca4808825dbccddde"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_U9hxV5YJMIOpr0FLkfLmXFZA|fc_000681f8252d408a0169f0d51da488819c8479d8fed76f397f", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1563 bytes to tests/src/io.netty/netty-all/4.0.23.Final/src/test/java/io_netty/netty_all/AbstractBootstrapInnerBootstrapChannelFactoryTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777390880105}]}
